name: Texas Rangers
description: A ragtag group of youngsters band together after the American Civil War to form the Texas Rangers, a group charged with the dangerous, ruthless duty of cleaning up the West.

review.author: eagl3f3ath3r
review.heading: LISTEN TO ME: this film is much better than most reviews give it credit
review.reviewBody: The acting is great, the director did a great job and its a cool, typical cowboy film. If you like westerns watch it, if not i recommend watching it on a friday night if your plans have collapsed. You wont regret it...trust me
